name: COMMONWEALTH of Pennsylvania, Respondent, v. Timothy McENANY, Petitioner

opinions.text:
ORDER
PER CURIAM.
AND NOW, this 30th day of August, 1996, the Petition for Allowance of Appeal is granted limited to the issue of the admissibility of Petitioner’s cellular phone, cellular phone memory chip and cellular phone records.
opinions.author: PER CURIAM.
